Start, stop, or inspect the messaging gateway. (Hermes parity: `hermes gateway`.)

Usage: gateway <COMMAND>

Commands:
  start   Start the messaging gateway in the foreground
  stop    Stop the running gateway daemon
  status  Show whether the gateway is running and which channels are attached
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
